# Tests for the dynamic equality operator

## Base types

```catala-metadata
#[test]
declaration scope TBase:
  output x content list of boolean
  output y content list of boolean

scope TBase:
  definition x equals [
    false = false;
    12 = 12;
    12.00 = 12.00;
    $12.12 = $12.12;
    |2021-01-01| = |2021-01-01|;
    1 year + 3 month + 2 day = 1 year + 3 month + 2 day
  ]

  assertion for all a among x we have a

  definition y equals [
    false = true;
    12 = 13;
    12.00 = 12.01;
    $12.12 = $12.13;
    |2021-01-01| = |2021-01-02|;
    1 year + 3 month = 1 year + 4 month
  ]

  assertion for all a among y we have not a
```


```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope TBase
┌─[RESULT]─ TBase ─
│ x = [true; true; true; true; true; true]
│ y = [false; false; false; false; false; false]
└─
```

```catala-metadata
#[test]
declaration scope TPoly:
  output x content list of boolean
  output y content list of boolean

scope TPoly:
  definition x equals [
#    Absent = Absent;
    Present content $12 = Present content $12;
#    [] = [];
    [ 1; 2; 3; 0 ] = [ 1; 2; 3; 0 ]
  ]

  assertion for all a among x we have a

  definition y equals [
    Absent = Present content 1;
    Present content $12 = Present content $13;
    [] = [12];
    [ 1; 2; 3; 0 ] = [ 1; 2; 3; 4 ];
    [ 1; 2; 3 ] = [ 1; 2; 3; 4 ]
  ]

  assertion for all a among y we have not a
```


```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope TPoly
┌─[RESULT]─ TPoly ─
│ x = [true; true]
│ y = [false; false; false; false; false]
└─
```

```catala-metadata
#[test]
declaration scope TTuple:
  output x content list of boolean
  output y content list of boolean

scope TTuple:
  definition x equals [
    (1, 2) = (1, 2);
    (1.12, 1.13, 14.1) = (1.12, 1.13, 14.1);
    (1, $2, 3.4, 365 day) = (1, $2, 3.4, 365 day);
    (1, (2, 3, 4), (5, 6), (7, (8, 9))) = (1, (2, 3, 4), (5, 6), (7, (8, 9)))
  ]

  assertion for all a among x we have a

  definition y equals [
    (1, 2) = (1, 3);
    (1.12, 1.13, 14.1) = (100.0, 1.13, 14.1);
    (1, $2, 3.4, 365 day) = (1, $2.1, 3.4, 365 day);
    (1, (2, 3, 4), (5, 6), (7, (8, 9))) =
      (1, (2, 3, 4), (5, 9), (7, (8, 9)))
  ]

  assertion for all a among y we have not a
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope TTuple
┌─[RESULT]─ TTuple ─
│ x = [true; true; true; true]
│ y = [false; false; false; false]
└─
```

```catala-metadata
declaration structure S:
  data f1 content boolean
  data f2 content decimal
  data f3 content list of (money, duration)

#[test]
declaration scope TStruct:
  output x content list of boolean
  output y content list of boolean

scope TStruct:
  definition x equals [
    S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] } = S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] };
    S { -- f1:false -- f2:1.0 --f3:[($1, 33 day); ($2, 66 day)] } = S { -- f1:false -- f2:1.0 --f3:[($1, 33 day); ($2, 66 day)] }
  ]

  assertion for all a among x we have a

  definition y equals [
    S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] } = S { -- f1:false -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] };
    S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] } = S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.1111 --f3:[] };
    S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[($1, 33 day)] } = S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] };
    S { -- f1:false -- f2:1.0 --f3:[($1, 33 day); ($2, 66 day)] } = S { -- f1:false -- f2:1.0 --f3:[($1, 33 day); ($2, 67 day)] }
  ]

  assertion for all a among y we have not a
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope TStruct
┌─[RESULT]─ TStruct ─
│ x = [true; true]
│ y = [false; false; false; false]
└─
```

```catala-metadata
declaration enumeration E:
  -- C0
  -- C1 content boolean
  -- C2 content decimal
  -- C3 content list of (money, duration)
  -- C4 content S

#[test]
declaration scope TEnum:
  output x content list of boolean
  output y content list of boolean

scope TEnum:
  definition x equals [
    C0 = C0;
    C1 content true = C1 content true;
    C2 content 42.0 = C2 content 42.0;
    C3 content [] = C3 content [];
    C3 content [($1, 33 day); ($2, 66 day)] = C3 content [($1, 33 day); ($2, 66 day)];
    C4 content S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] } = C4 content S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] }
  ]

  assertion for all a among x we have a

  definition y equals [
    C0 = C1 content false;
    C1 content false = C2 content 12.12;
    C1 content true = C1 content false;
    C2 content 42.0 = C2 content 0.0;
    C3 content [] = C3 content [($1, 33 day)];
    C3 content [($1, 33 day); ($2, 66 day)] = C3 content [($1, 33 day); ($2, 67 day)];
    C4 content S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.111 --f3:[] } = C4 content S { -- f1:true -- f2:1.11 --f3:[] }
  ]

  assertion for all a among y we have not a
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope TEnum
┌─[RESULT]─ TEnum ─
│ x = [true; true; true; true; true; true]
│ y = [false; false; false; false; false; false; false]
└─
```
